{"tid":125364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正男死前照曝光　大馬當局拘一北韓男子　指在場監視暗殺過程","createTime":"2017-02-18T11:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T17:17:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cbdaf3025f12c9c741fcd2021fa6487396b3103","tid":125364,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kim_1tz7y_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkim_1tz7y_1200x0.png&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=effb5f72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkim_1tz7y_1200x0.png&h=d8dac45a\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kim_1tz7y_1200x0.png</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓領袖金正恩同父異母哥哥金正男被殺案，馬來西亞警方再拘捕一名北韓男子，指其在案發現場附近監視行凶過程，另正緝捕三名北韓男疑犯。同時，金正男死因未能確定，要進行第二次解剖。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大馬媒體《新海峽時報》刊出一張金正男遇刺後在吉隆坡機場診療室拍的照片，顯示他坐在椅上，似已失去知覺，沒有表面傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞警方在周五晚，突擊搜查一間公寓，拘捕涉嫌與暗殺案有關的46歲男子。被捕男子譯音為李勇哲，持有北韓護照，並有當地政府發出的外地勞工簽證，曾多次往來馬來西亞和印尼。當局正調查他是否案件主謀。<br />\n<br />\n警方早前已拘捕兩名涉嫌向金正男噴灑有毒液體的女疑犯，她們分別持有越南及印尼護照。至於早前被捕的馬來西亞男子，相信與案件無關。<br />\n<br />\n《新海峽時報》引消息指，警方早前發布了涉案四名男子的機場閉路電視畫面，懷疑他們是北韓特工，發現四人全程近距離監視兩名女疑犯行兇。當中三人當日在距離案發現場約50米的餐廳守候，另一人則跟蹤金正男。據消息，他們跟蹤金正男已近一年。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，金正男的死因仍未確定，要進行第二次解剖。北韓駐馬來西亞大使周五晚再到醫院要求領回遺體，但被拒絕。他表示，北韓不接受大馬的驗屍結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/金正男死前照曝光-大馬當局拘一北韓男子-在場監視暗殺過程/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E7%94%B7%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-%E5%9C%A8%E5%A0%B4%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%E6%9A%97%E6%AE%BA%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%2F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1d0dc37c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E7%94%B7%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90-%E5%9C%A8%E5%A0%B4%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%E6%9A%97%E6%AE%BA%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%2F&h=86f8a1e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/金正男死前照曝光-大馬當局拘一北韓男子-在場監視暗殺過程/</a>"},{"pid":"ca719145b120226f097334db2f65f21557911fc6","tid":125364,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"同我平時打完J個姿勢咁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c621d724251c054d9ece648d98a5c23045ffe475","tid":125364,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我平時打完J個姿勢咁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小心身體"},{"pid":"45943a55b7bab37de8fa186b5ec3803226d08edd","tid":125364,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8bffb8917d25d6d34fcaa61a4ce273e7264769","tid":125364,"uid":17216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我平時打完J個姿勢咁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b24d832e0c7a1781b46d216cd0638159f53b38c","tid":125364,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我平時打完J個姿勢咁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n虧就唔好學人打啦"},{"pid":"d96c13bbb65396ebd3b5a9b15e2e10ad